                started.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
          <div class="card card-block m-b-10">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-3 ">
                <div class="interview-image">
                  <a target="_blank" href="http://exidea.co.jp">
                    <%= image_tag("exidea-logo.jpg", height: '80', width: '80') %>
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-9 about-me-card">
                <div><b>Web Director(Intern)</b><span style="color: #666"> / May 2016 – Mar 2017</span></div>
                I launched new web media from scratch. The media contributed to $80,000 in sales per
                month 6 months after I launched it.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card card-block m-b-10">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-3 ">
                <div class="interview-image">
                  <a target="_blank" href="http://www.miloenterprises.ca/">
                    <%= image_tag("milo-enterprises-logo.png", height: '80', width: '80') %>
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-9 about-me-card">
                <div><b>Degital Marketer</b><span style="color: #666"> / May 2017 – Now</span></div>
                My responsibility is to manage an online shop on Amazon and Rakuten. I'm taking care of most of the work
                all the way from marketing stuff(copywriting, promotion, ads, etc.), shipment managiment, site design to customer service.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
